TEXT.S: = M'ihu = Gaga mniq Tayungsu Hpingcyu ka alang M'ihu. 208 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 526 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 79% niqan 413 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 21% niqan 113 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 69%, Amis 2%, Bunun 1%, Paiwan 2%, Saysiyat 1%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 1%, ni rahuq na o 3%.
